==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lipogram
<hw>Lip"o*gram</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧p"⟦osl⟧*gr⟦acr⟧m; 277)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>lei`pein</grk>, <grk>lipei^n</grk>, to
leave, omit + <ets>-gram</ets>.]</ety> <def>A writing composed of words
not having a certain letter or letters; -- as in the Odyssey of
Tryphiodorus there was no A in the first book, no B in the second, and
so on.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lipogrammatic</ent>⟦br⟧
